  <brief_title>Whole Body Vibration Exercise Training for Institutionalized Elderly</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effects of Whole Body Vibration Exercise Training on Physical Functioning and Falls in Institutionalized Elderly: a Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
